data.name: XReferenceResolvedBroadcaster
desc: This interface is used to manipulate reference resolved listener.

methods.name: addReferenceResolvedListener
desc: Adds a new reference resolved listener for an element collector.
When the element collector has completely collected that element, this listener will receive a notification.

methods.name: removeReferenceResolvedListener
desc: Removes a listener from an element collector.
When a listener is removed, it will not receive notification when collection completes.
